# PR Lifecycle conventions

Read `AGENTS.md` for full instructions.

- Policy lives in `policy/pr-lifecycle.yml`; change policy before changing closure logic
- Human PRs: warn before close; bot PRs: stricter auto-close allowed
- Security: Tier 1 block secrets; Tier 2 CI flag; Tier 3 lifecycle labels only
- Prefer `make` targets; run `make verify-harness` after scaffold changes
